<DOC><DOCNO> WSJ870312-0131 </DOCNO><HL> Dividend News:Hovnanian Enterprises Inc.</HL><DD> 03/12/87</DD><SO>  </SO><IN> HOVDIVIDENDS (DIV) </IN><TEXT>   HOVNANIAN ENTERPRISES INC., Red Bank, N.J., declared a 2-for-1 stock split, payable April 13. The company set a March 23 record date, but said purchasers of common through April 13 also will be entitled to the stock split. The residential real estate developer said the split is intended to improve the trading liquidity of the stock. The company has about three million shares outstanding. </TEXT></DOC>